            <title><![CDATA[【#颈椎病患者夏季别让空调直吹肩颈#[裂开]】#夏季是最容易诱发颈椎病的季节#。医生提醒，预防颈椎病要养成良好的习惯，不要受凉，不要老低头，低头刷手机或学习...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%A2%88%E6%A4%8E%E7%97%85%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E5%A4%8F%E5%AD%A3%E5%88%AB%E8%AE%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%B0%83%E7%9B%B4%E5%90%B9%E8%82%A9%E9%A2%88%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%A2%88%E6%A4%8E%E7%97%85%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E5%A4%8F%E5%AD%A3%E5%88%AB%E8%AE%A9%E7%A9%BA%E8%B0%83%E7%9B%B4%E5%90%B9%E8%82%A9%E9%A2%88%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#颈椎病患者夏季别让空调直吹肩颈#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[裂开]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fc_liekai-9df295d44f.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A4%8F%E5%AD%A3%E6%98%AF%E6%9C%80%E5%AE%B9%E6%98%93%E8%AF%B1%E5%8F%91%E9%A2%88%E6%A4%8E%E7%97%85%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%A3%E8%8A%82%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%A4%8F%E5%AD%A3%E6%98%AF%E6%9C%80%E5%AE%B9%E6%98%93%E8%AF%B1%E5%8F%91%E9%A2%88%E6%A4%8E%E7%97%85%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%A3%E8%8A%82%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#夏季是最容易诱发颈椎病的季节#</span></a>。医生提醒，预防颈椎病要养成良好的习惯，不要受凉，不要老低头，低头刷手机或学习看电脑30分钟，要站起来晃晃、摇头晃脑，别让肌肉长期保持一个姿势。而本身颈椎就有问题的患者，不要让空调或电扇直吹颈肩部，特别是后枕部，在冷气很足的办公室，建议在脖子上搭一条围巾。（科普中国） <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4928911080095758" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">江苏新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/001q6ELGly8hgdyqat9fmj61hc0u0dkn02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/RAxjzqVVlx087ohzgHBm01041200jpud0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1690837975&amp;ssig=IyGwwTY3aL&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/uRuuy68ulx087ohy081a01041200a0Ay0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1690837975&amp;ssig=NOxKGJRT8L&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/pmD79tN0lx087ohxvwfm010412006k5F0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1690837975&amp;ssig=LoB8ujmRXW&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4928911080095758&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
